lines.text: HEMOGLOBIN A1C (HEMOGLOBIN A1C, DIAGNOSTIC) - Final result (11/26/2012 11:06 AM PST)
A repeatable Hb Alc > or = 6.5% is
diagnostic of diabetes. A single Hb Alc >
or = 6.5% can also be confirmed by a fasting
random plasma glucose > or = 200 mg/dl, or a
2 hour oral glucose tolerance test result >
or = 200 mg/dl. Patients with Hb Alc of
5.7-6.4% are at increased risk for future
